headline: The Hartford’s New Research Finds Continued Need Among Gen Z Workers For Mental Health Care
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., May 01, 2025--The Hartford’s 2025 research shows 40% of Gen Z workers feel depressed or anxious at least a few times per week and 46% say stigma prevents care
